---
title: Beef and Poblano Bowls with Black Beans and Rice
description: This hearty bowl will transport you to a west-coast taqueria! We've packed everything we can into this one: beef, black beans, poblanos and savoury rice! And it doesn't stop there. We're topping this number of with lime crema, salsa and feta!
